### Narrative Engine API Test

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Create Novel
# @name create_novel
POST {{host}}/novels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "인터넷에서 다운받은 txt임",
  "author": "모름",
  "description": "이 정보 어디서 얻을 수 있나??"
}

### 3. Process Novel
# novel_id는 위 소설 생성 결과에서 얻은 ID를 사용해야 합니다.
@novel_id = f17dcaa0-849b-487d-9e39-ae6c917e8a69
POST {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="text"

1화 - 응 고백했습니다...
--boundary--

### 4. Analyze Scene (Single Scene)
POST {{host}}/analyze-scene
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "novel_id": "test-novel-uuid",
  "scene_index": 0,
  "text": "주인공 김철수가 숲속에서 길을 잃었다. 그는 주변을 둘러보며 당황해하고 있다."
}

### 5. List Characters in Novel
GET {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}/characters
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get Character Detail
# character_id는 캐릭터 조회 결과에서 얻은 ID를 사용해야 합니다.
@character_id = 0f438606-0fef-4c34-bc3f-0fc16ac5f313
GET {{host}}/characters/{{character_id}}
Accept: application/json

### 7. Delete Novel
DELETE {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}
Accept: application/json

### 8. Generate Image for Scene
# scene_id는 분석 결과에서 얻은 ID를 사용해야 합니다.
@scene_id = 388bc6bc-109e-4705-8815-f4b01b56360b
POST {{host}}/scenes/{{scene_id}}/generate-image
Accept: application/json

### 9. List Novels
GET {{host}}/novels
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get Novel Detail
GET {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}
Accept: application/json

### 11. List Scenes in Novel
GET {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}/scenes
Accept: application/json

### 11a. Get Novel Content
GET {{host}}/novels/{{novel_id}}/content
Accept: application/json

### 12. Get Scene Detail
GET {{host}}/scenes/{{scene_id}}
Accept: application/json

### 13. Get Character Relationships
GET {{host}}/characters/{{character_id}}/relationships
Accept: application/json
